    "description": "BikeDekho Advisory Limited, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a E-commerce Executive for our Madurai operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout BikeDekho Advisory Limited:\nBikeDekho Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in A/B Testing\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Magento\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Flexible working hours\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Madurai, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with BikeDekho Advisory Limited!",
